OL,5, More than #420m from a pension scheme  
OL,6, for mineworkers has flowed into the    
OL,7, government's coffers in the past three 
OL,8, years, the BBC can reveal.             
OL,10,FThe government is entitled to half the 
OL,11,Fsurplus cash from the scheme under an  
OL,12,Fagreement signed 30 years ago.         
OL,14,FLabour says the deal is unfair to      
OL,15,Fformer miners and their families.      
OL,17,FShadow minister Ed Miliband says Labour
OL,18,Fwill review the agreement if it wins   
OL,19,Fpower to "deliver the justice to which 
OL,20,Fminers are entitled".                  
